findings.title: State variable visibility is not set (SWC-108)
findings.description: Specify variables as public, internal, or private.

findings.title: Owner can set fee up to 100%
findings.description: The contract owner has the ability to set fees up to 100%, which could potentially lead to unfair or malicious behavior.

findings.title: Owner can set max tx limit up to 100%
findings.description: The owner has the ability to set the maximum transaction limit up to 100%, which could potentially pause trading.
